    "text": "B4 Number the games 1, . . , 2011, and let A = (ajk) be the 2011 × 2011 matrix whose jk entry is 1 if player k wins game j and i = √−1 if player k loses game j. Then ahja jk is 1 if players h and k tie in game j; i if player h wins and player k loses in game j; and —i if h loses and k wins. It follows that T + iW = AT A.",
